column2:
'Description'
'Enale Application Insights'
'diagnostics and data'
'collection'
'Whether to enale Azure Application Insights to collect'
'data from the deployed endpoints.'
'By default: false.'
'Scoring timeout'
'A timeout in milliseconds to enforce for scoring calls to the'
'we service.'
'By default: 60000.'
'Auto scale enaled'
'Whether to enale autoscaling for the we service.'
'By default: true.'
'Min replicas'
'The minimum numer of containers to use when'
'autoscaling this we service.'
'By default: 1.'
